modules.description: Provides functions to create, modify, and export triangular meshes, including bindings to external mesh generation tools. Operates on mesh data structures that represent geometric surfaces through nodes, edges, and triangles. Enables exporting mesh data to LaTeX, SciLab, and other scientific computing environments for visualization and analysis.

Provides methods to compute normal vectors, area, and centroid of triangular faces, and to extract vertex indices from a mesh structure. Works with triangle-based mesh data, including vertex positions and connectivity information. Used to analyze geometric properties of 3D models and prepare mesh data for rendering or simulation.
